<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">غ ص ن:</span> <span class="c2">(الْغُصْنُ)</span> غُصْنُ الشَّجَرِ وَجَمْعُهُ <span class="c2">(أَغْصَانٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(غُصُونٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(غِصَنَةٌ)</span> مِثْلُ قُرْطٍ وَقِرَطَةٍ. وَ <span class="c2">(غَصَنَ الْغُصْنَ)</span> قَطَعَهُ وَبَابُهُ ضَرَبَ. وَأَبُو <span class="c2">(الْغُصْنِ)</span> كُنْيَةُ جُحَى.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>